    <briefdescription>
<para>Static singleton for CAN sub-node (<ref refid="namespacePanelGroup" kindref="compound">PanelGroup</ref>) firmware. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Reads node_id from the PA0 strap pin at boot, configures the CAN receive filter for CTRL_BCAST and TEST_SEQ frames, dispatches incoming frames to registered <ref refid="namespaceOpenSkyhawk" kindref="compound">OpenSkyhawk</ref> output objects, polls registered input objects, and sends heartbeat frames every 500 ms.</para>
<para>Node ID strapping: tie PA0 to 3.3 V for node_id=1; leave floating (internal pull-down) for node_id=2. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
